# Schema: provenance orphan refusal SHACL shape
@prefix sh: <http://www.w3.org/ns/shacl#> .
:OrphanRefusalShape a sh:NodeShape ;
  sh:targetClass :ProvNode ;
  sh:property [ sh:path :wasDerivedFrom ; sh:minCount 1 ] .
# A SHACL validator MUST enforce this shape: every ProvNode that lacks wasDerivedFrom
# MUST fail conformance (a gate that blocks). This requires a running validator to check.
